9
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,120
♪Words fall too short♪

10
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:50,040
♪So I ride far♪

11
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,780
♪To chase the dream beyond the skyline♪

12
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,200
♪No regret♪

13
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,790
♪Through the flow of years♪

14
