♪But fate cries loud♪

18
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Envying a world too pure to keep♪

19
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:07,580
♪Seasons bloom, yet lips grow weak♪

20
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:09,850
♪Through dust of time, all mortals stray♪

21
