613
00:31:08,270 --> 00:31:09,110
Prince Rui!

614
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,640
(Mingde Gate)
We obey the emperor's orders.

615
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,720
No full tiger tally, no mobilization.

616
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:14,070
Rules are rules.

617
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:19,910
Disaster!

618
00:31:20,030 --> 00:31:20,870
Disaster!

619
00:31:22,500 --> 00:31:24,350
Marshal Wei is massing the Cavalry
and Infantry Commands

620
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,310
at the gates.

621
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,550
Prince Rui persuades them

622
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,480
to save the day.

623
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:28,640
Marshal is back?

624
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,750
Report this to Prince Yu

625
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:31,880
and Eunuch Lin at once.

626
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:33,240
We've ordered someone

627
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:34,160
to tell Prince Yu.

628
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,480
What's your plan?

629
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:39,030
Where's Lu Chang?

630
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,510
They'll meet Prince Yu in the hall.

631
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:42,110
I'm looking for the tiger tally.

632
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:44,680
He is courting death.

633
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,110
Prince Yu is holding Mingshu

634
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:47,400
hostage to threaten him.

635
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,480
In that case,

636
00:31:48,790 --> 00:31:49,830
please reveal the location

637
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:51,590
of the tiger tally.

638
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:53,440
Prince Yu has hidden it.

639
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,880
No one knows where.

640
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:56,240
This...

641
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,000
If you find it,

642
00:31:58,350 --> 00:31:59,270
I swear

643
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:01,200
to deliver it to Prince Rui.

644
00:32:04,110 --> 00:32:04,950
Okay.

645
00:32:07,350 --> 00:32:08,750
Start your search there.

646
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:20,790
Eunuch Lin,

647
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,830
Prince Rui and Marshal

648
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:23,000
are gathering at the gates.

649
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:25,240
Don't panic.

650
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,510
Even if Marshal returns,

651
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:29,880
Prince Rui has only
half of the tiger tally.

652
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:32,000
They can't command both commands.

653
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,750
Who was that?

654
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:46,300
She came to send pastries.

655
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,190
Brother,

656
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,350
how was your trip

657
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:18,350
to Ning'an for Nanny Lin's birthday?

658
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,030
I couldn't go in person.

659
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:21,550
Was it

660
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,240
great?

661
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:43,870
Guards!

662
00:33:53,110 --> 00:33:54,070
Lu Chang.

663
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,150
That's right,

664
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:56,270
it's me.

665
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,440
(Where would Prince Yu)

666
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:17,670
(hide the tiger tally?)

667
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,150
Where is Cao Hai?

668
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:36,110
General Cao is dead.

669
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:43,110
My followers

670
00:34:43,110 --> 00:34:44,590
will not die in vain.

671
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,800
Prince Rui

672
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,630
and his faction

673
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:50,800
will perish.

674
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:54,000
As for you, Lu Chang,

675
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,510
submit

676
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,150
and obey me now,

677
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:00,880
then you'll

678
00:35:01,420 --> 00:35:02,320
have glory

679
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:04,670
under my rule.

680
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,630
But if you persist in your madness,

681
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,550
you can see the end.

682
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,670
Prince Yu, you seek my allegiance?

683
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:16,000
Let's discuss it.

684
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,280
As an emperor,

685
00:35:19,070 --> 00:35:20,880
how would you surpass Prince Rui?

686
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,670
I know

687
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:30,680
you are testing my stance on reforms.

688
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:33,870
I know reforms are inevitable,

689
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,190
but conservatives

690
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,530
dominate the court.

691
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:38,920
I must consolidate military power

692
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:40,880
before enthronement.

693
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,360
After all,

694
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:43,880
gradual steps

695
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,030
lead to greatness.

696
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:48,190
Prince Yu, according to you,

697
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:50,480
sacrificing loyal subjects

698
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,630
and raising private armies

699
00:35:53,030 --> 00:35:54,230
for personal gain

700
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,960
are merely incremental strategies
to consolidate power?

701
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,320
But I believe that

702
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:02,440
power gained
through the blood of the innocent

703
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,630
will inevitably demand more sacrifice

704
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,440
to sustain itself.

705
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,760
Such a ruler

706
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,920
would only bring disaster to Da'an.

707
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:18,840
Lu Chang,

708
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,840
I have shown you ample courtesy.

709
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:23,290
Now that the entire capital

710
00:36:23,290 --> 00:36:24,510
is under my control,

711
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:25,960
what leverage do you have?

712
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,150
The throne of Da'an

713
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,700
can't be occupied by anyone
without virtue.

714
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,920
It's not yours now,

715
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:35,550
nor will it ever be.

716
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:43,440
I'm tired

717
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:45,670
of your futility.

718
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:51,480
I can't bear to see your blood
stain the hall.

719
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:54,710
So boring.

720
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:56,550
Enough empty words.

721
00:36:57,070 --> 00:36:57,920
Where is Mingshu?

722
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:10,230
(It looks like Lady Su
found the tiger tally.)

723
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:14,190
Eunuch Lin!

724
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,960
When will you

725
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:20,000
summon the physician

726
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,710
for me?

727
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:23,480
I've made it clear.

728
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:25,630
It can be negotiated.

729
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:27,630
Now, Prince Rui is

730
00:37:27,630 --> 00:37:29,490
assembling the two commands
outside the palace.

731
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:31,960
If you can bring

732
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:34,110
Prince Rui's half of the tiger tally,

733
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,000
I'll get you

734
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,510
the best imperial physician.

735
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,190
If you remain obstinate,

736
00:37:42,150 --> 00:37:44,480
don't blame me for being ruthless.

737
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,200
Director,

738
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:48,760
consider your options.

739
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:54,280
Eunuch Lin,

740
00:37:55,150 --> 00:37:56,150
I'll help

741
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:57,800
Prince Yu

742
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,710
persuade Prince Rui.

743
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:00,880
Really?

744
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:04,070
Director,

745
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,510
how are you going to convince him?

746
00:38:06,550 --> 00:38:07,630
No need

747
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,550
to worry.

748
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:12,320
Years at court

749
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:14,230
have honed

750
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:15,800
nothing

751
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,400
but my silver tongue.

752
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,640
Alternatively,

753
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:19,710
you can allow me

754
00:38:19,710 --> 00:38:21,630
to take Noble Consort Hua

755
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,440
as a hostage.

756
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,670
If Prince Rui resists,

757
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:27,760
he becomes a traitor.

758
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,200
But

759
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,960
after that,

760
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:37,190
I demand

761
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:38,920
to remain

762
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,480
in power

763
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:43,030
until

764
00:38:43,150 --> 00:38:44,280
I retire.

765
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:46,360
Eunuch Lin,

766
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:48,030
what do you think?

767
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,590
Success

768
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,190
makes all things

769
00:38:53,550 --> 00:38:55,280
possible.

770
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:00,600
Guards.

771
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:02,920
Escort

772
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:03,920
Director

773
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:05,030
and Noble Consort Hua

774
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,400
to the gates.

775
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,600
Yes.

776
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,240
Wait.

777
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:10,840
Eunuch Lin,

778
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:11,960
persuasion

779
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,550
requires gravity.

780
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:14,880
Let me

781
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,590
compose myself

782
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,000
to show solemnity.

783
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,150
Besides,

784
00:39:19,150 --> 00:39:20,960
if I go there like this,

785
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:23,000
it seems I've been coerced by you.

786
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:24,480
They won't believe me.

787
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:26,550
Please allow me

788
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:28,070
to prepare myself in the side chamber.

789
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,590
Just a moment.

790
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,800
Release me!

791
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:47,030
Mingshu!

792
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:47,870
Lu Chang!

793
00:39:51,670 --> 00:39:52,510
Mingshu!

794
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,260
Retrieve half of the tiger tally

795
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:59,360
from Prince Rui's possession for me,

796
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:00,680
and I may

797
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,400
spare her life.

798
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:10,870
Lu Chang...

799
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:13,510
Prince Yu is wreaking havoc.

800
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,070
Cao Hai has slaughtered

801
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:16,190
the Jian Family for him.

802
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,550
If you care about me,

803
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,840
don't give in!

804
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,400
Otherwise, I'll never forgive you.

805
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,000
Do you hear me?

806
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,120
Is that so?

807
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:27,960
Really?

808
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:58,580
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

809
00:40:58,580 --> 00:41:01,120
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

810
00:41:02,350 --> 00:41:05,000
♪As time quietly slips away♪

811
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:08,080
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

