00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:26,250
♪With love that outlasts all♪

817
00:41:27,660 --> 00:41:30,200
♪Together we'll traverse♪

818
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:33,380
♪Through grandeur and adversity♪

819
00:41:34,140 --> 00:41:36,600
♪When clarity arrives♪

820
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:40,010
♪Destiny's threads entwine,
