♪Through years with sincere love♪

825
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:58,880
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

826
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:02,450
♪Counting endless nights♪

827
00:42:02,450 --> 00:42:04,580
♪Yet never your♪

